query:
-- Ver detalhes dos enrichment runs
SELECT 
  id,
  status,
  started_at,
  paused_at,
  completed_at,
  error_message,
  TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, started_at, COALESCE(paused_at, completed_at)) as duracao_minutos
FROM enrichment_runs
WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM enrichment_runs ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 3);
